snippet.title: Gameplay: Sewermania (Milton Bradley, 1983) for the TI-99/4A (with speech!)
snippet.description:
This is a demonstration of gameplay from the game Sewermania for the TI-99/4A home computer and (optionally) Milton Bradley MBX.  

This gameplay demonstration was done on original hardware using an F18A modded TI-99/4A with Speech Synth module.


#ti994a #retrocomputing #texasinstruments
